column2:
ggplot() + 
  geom_dumbbell(
    data=b10, 
    aes(y=reorder(TeamFull, season_team_ator), x=season_team_ator, xend=season_opp_ator),
    size = 2,
    linewidth = 1,
    color = "grey",
    colour_x = "green",
    colour_xend = "red") + 
  theme_minimal()+
  labs(
    y= "Team",
    x = "2022-2023 Assist to turnover ratio",
    title = "Maryland had much better ball control than its opponents last season"
  )
